column.name: UMREGION
column.comment:
Region code depending on the database in CableMaster, where the data is extracted from.
Valid values: NRW, HSN, KBW

column.name: WOSTA
column.comment:
Workorder COMPLETION STATUS.
Default value = ' '
Required for GigaKombi bundling process

column.name: WOECYY
column.comment:
Order Entry Date (Year)
(3 digit year delta starting from 1900)   
DATE ENTERED YY.
Default value = 0
Required for GigaKombi bundling process.

column.name: WOEMM
column.comment:
Order Entry Date (Month)
(2 digit numeric month )
DATE ENTERED MM.
Default value = 0
Required for GigaKombi bundling process

column.name: WOEDD
column.comment:
Order Entry Date (Day)
(2 digit day)
DATE ENTERED DD.
Default value = 0
Required for GigaKombi bundling process

column.name: WOETM
column.comment:
TIME ENTERED.
Default value = 0
Required for GigaKombi bundling process.

column.name: WOCU_NUM
column.comment:
Customer number.
Default value = 0
Required for GigaKombi bundling process

column.name: WOPSF
column.comment: NUM OF PRI PAY FROM COMM

column.name: WOPST
column.comment: NUM OF PRI PAY TO COMM

column.name: WOASF
column.comment: NUM OF ADL PAY FROM COMM

column.name: WOAST
column.comment: NUM OF ADL PAY TO COMM

column.name: WORTDTT
column.comment: Related install order for trouble tickets

column.name: WORTDTTH
column.comment: Related install history sequence for trouble ticke
